# install parcel and tape

## developing with parcel

> npm install -g parcel parcel
> npm run dev 

then, in a browser, open: http://localhost:1234

## testing via tape

> npm install tape --save-dev
> npm run test

Here are some useful tape method:

> assert          deepEqual     deepEquals        deepLooseEqual
> doesNotEqual    doesNotMatch  doesNotThrow      equal
> equals          error         fail              ifErr
> ifError         iferror       is                isEqual
> isEquivalent    isInequal     isInequivalent    isNot
> isNotDeepEqual  isNotDeeply   isNotEqual        isNotEquivalent
> looseEqual      looseEquals   match             not
> notDeepEqual    notDeepEquals notDeepLooseEqual notDeeply
> notEqual        notEquals     notEquivalent     notLooseEqual
> notLooseEquals  notOk         notSame           notStrictEqual
> notStrictEquals notok         ok                pass
> same            skip          strictEqual       strictEquals
 
## build with parcel-bundler

> npm install -g parcel-bundler 
> npm run build

